 Faster, cheaper, cozier... the #China-Laos Railway has won the hearts of many Lao overseas students in China. The railway "makes me feel at home," they said. Shuttling between China's southwest Kunming and Lao capital Vientiane, the train has made commutes and trade in the region easier. Click for more. #GLOBALink  Produced by Xinhua Global Service.â– 